2b2t is a hostile mining dimension[[footnote]]Mining dimensions are dimensions that are intended to be stripped for resources, allowing you to gather materials without making the landscape of your main world look ugly. [[/footnote]], overrun by the [[[Invisible Mafia]]].

------

The 2000 block radius around 0,0 is the 
true spawn of 2b2t, taken from this world 
download.

