------

++ Biomes
This dimension contains every vanilla biome, from the overworld, the nether and the end. They generate in an infinite checkerboard pattern, allowing you to continue to strip resources.


------

++ Structures
The overworld contains a huge amount of structures, with custom built ones primarily located closer to spawn, and naturally generating ones occurring everywhere.

